# Binary assets — never apply end-of-line conversion. Without this, a clone on a
# machine with core.autocrlf=true would smudge LF->CRLF inside these files and
# corrupt them (notably the ASU working-paper PDF and the result/equity PNGs).
*.pdf binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.ico binary
*.parquet binary
*.gz binary

# Keep text/code line endings stable across platforms (LF in the repo).
*.py text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.txt text eol=lf
